00:19:30.969 --> 00:19:33.038
We don't have a good read on that. Okay.

00:19:33.038 --> 00:19:37.676
If we're thinking about the grocery store,
those boxes turn over very quickly.

00:19:37.876 --> 00:19:41.380
Having worked in the industry, the box is
going to get made at the box plant.

