The second we'll talk about right sizing.

00:21:24.883 --> 00:21:27.886
So first when we think about consumers

00:21:28.487 --> 00:21:30.956
Walmarts targets

00:21:30.956 --> 00:21:33.959
Amazon Home Depot, they are consumers.

00:21:33.992 --> 00:21:37.496
And the majority of boxes
that are made are intended for them,

00:21:38.597 --> 00:21:40.065
not for us.

00:21:40.065 --> 00:21:43.068
In fact, that's why they call them big box
